latestIgtvVideos.title: Review : @tefalindia Pro-Style Garment Steamer
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I am the kind of person who likes getting dressed up for myself. I know all of us are staying indoors for our safety, but this should not stop us from feeling beautiful in our own homes. To be like me and get your pretty clothes ready, the Tefal Pro-Style Garment Steamer is the ideal product. It has a high performance with 1800W for professional steaming at home and generates steam in just 45 seconds. Its 3 levels of steam output (30g/min) gives effortless steaming even for the delicate clothes and the vertical support gives maximum comfort for single-handed press and steam. It is a must-have product for times like these as it can also sanitize clothes by killing all the germs, bacteria, mites, odors, pollen, and allergens. It is very gentle on fabric and there's no risk of burning, tearing, or damaging your clothes. So be your own cheerleader and click on the link in my stories to get the Tefal Pro-style garment steamer.

latestIgtvVideos.title: The Nikaah #QuboolHai #HansUpForSRK
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Nikaah ~ a ceremony said to bind two souls together in the act of marriage 💕 . 

Reminiscing every moment , from Ohaila being the flower girl, to my dad waiting to walk me down the aisle , to me entering with the Ayat - Al - Kursi (a religious script to ward off all evil ) held above me by my brothers ,  my dearest mother tearing up while praying for my happiness and a stolen glance from the love of my life as I walk towards him only to say #QuboolHai 

Surrounded by love and happiness under the twilight skies I watched my dream wedding unfold into reality a month ago and have waited to share every moment with you guys ♥️☺️.
